  "reference_number": "INU0310",
  "remarks": "\nThe Nuclear Fuel Production Division (NFPC) is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: The Nuclear Fuel Production Division is associated with the Atomic Energy Organization of Iran, who is or has been responsible for, providing support for, or facilitating the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.\n",
